description: Log reproduction rate for COTS (year^-1); exp(log_r_COTS) gives reproduction rate.
Log mortality rate for COTS (year^-1); exp(log_m_COTS) gives mortality rate.
Log intrinsic growth rate for slow coral (year^-1); exp(log_growth_slow) gives growth rate.
Log intrinsic growth rate for fast coral (year^-1); exp(log_growth_fast) gives growth rate.
Log carrying capacity for slow coral; exp(log_K_slow) gives the carrying capacity (coral cover units).
Log carrying capacity for fast coral; exp(log_K_fast) gives the carrying capacity (coral cover units).
Log half-saturation constant for coral predation effects; exp(log_half_sat) gives the constant.
Log environmental modifier (unitless) affecting COTS reproduction efficiency; exp(log_env) gives multiplier.
Log standard deviation for COTS observations; exp(log_sd_COTS) gives standard deviation.
Log standard deviation for slow coral observations; exp(log_sd_slow) gives standard deviation.
Log standard deviation for fast coral observations; exp(log_sd_fast) gives standard deviation.
